{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "23", "m": "07", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "15", "M": "45", "S": "39"}}, "news": [{"title": "SC defers hearing on plea seeking refund for homebuyers in Supertech twin towers case", "para": "The Supreme Court has postponed a hearing on Supertech twin-towers homebuyers' refund plea. Efforts are underway to satisfy claims for those not opting for alternative allotments. The court granted three months to explore further options for homebuyers' satisfaction. Homebuyers are not receiving refunds, with last payments made in 2024. The twin-towers in Noida were demolished on August 28, 2022.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/regulatory/supreme-court-postpones-homebuyers-refund-hearing-in-supertech-twin-towers-case/132583346?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-279710/132583346.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "regulatory"}, {"title": "Mahindra Lifespaces' net profit rises 67% to \u20b985.55 crore in Q1 FY27", "para": "Mahindra Lifespaces' consolidated total income increased to \u20b9977.54 crore during the quarter. Residential pre-sales more than doubled to \u20b9925 crore, while gross development value additions stood at \u20b95,600 crore.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/mahindra-lifespaces-reports-67-surge-in-q1-fy27-net-profit-to-8555-crore/132578021?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-185049/132578021.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}, {"title": "Knowledge Realty Trust revenue up over 16%, EBITDA & NOI rise 18% since IPO: CEO", "para": "Knowledge Realty Trust has recorded over 16% revenue growth and 18% growth in EBITDA and net operating income since its IPO, said Shirish Godbole, CEO, Knowledge Realty Trust. The REIT has 92% occupancy, 2.6 million sq ft under development and 18% leverage, which it plans to use for future acquisitions.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/commercial/knowledge-realty-trust-reports-strong-financial-growth-post-ipo/132576399?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-60654/132576399.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "commercial"}]}